# 3. Use of Microservices Architecture


## Status
accepted


## Context
Startups have a high pace of change leading to new features. 
This leads to a requirement of modularity that enables addition of new fetaures that don't adversly impact current features and functionality.

There are many alternative architecture styles like monolithic, tiered, Microservices etc


## Decision

### Design decision
We will use microservices architecture

### Design Justification
Microservices architecture enable ease of adding new features as modules"


## Consequences
We will need additionally skilled personnel that are knowledgable on microservices pattern and tools
